This interface is the cross platform version of the java lang Cloneable interface p It is part of our effort to provide support for both 2SE and 2ME platforms Under this scheme classes need to implement CloneableCompatibility instead of java lang Cloneable p p Note java lang Cloneable is not part of CLDC p
